node.text: As a boy growing up in rural France, Julien Roure wanted to make guitars for his heroes. Thanks to a punk rock attitude, single-minded vision and hard work, today his custom-made instruments are played by rock stars worldwide. How far will you go to achieve your dream? What’s your custom guitar? Link in bio. #DreamersOn
